invalid type: string "Safety equipment\nLights:When riding at night, you must use a white front\nlight and red rear reflector (a rear-facing flashing red light,\nlike an LED, is okay too). Reflectors and reflective tape on\nyour helmet,\nclothes or\nbicycle also\nmake you more\nvisible.\nHorn: Attach a\nhorn or bell to\nyour handle\nbars and use it\nto warn\npedestrians and\nother vehicles\naffic;